      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Looking for a dependable and well-cared-for ride? This car is in good condition and is ready to hit the road with its next owner! It has been well-maintained, offering a smooth driving experience and a clean look that really stands out. It's a fantastic choice for anyone seeking a reliable vehicle that still has plenty of great miles ahead!",
