    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is being offered in poor condition and is best suited for a mechanic, a dedicated restoration enthusiast, or someone in need of a donor car for parts. The engine is currently non-operational due to a significant internal failure, and the transmission shows signs of heavy slipping. Additionally, the exterior has several deep scratches and minor dents, while the interior upholstery requires a complete overhaul due to significant tearing and staining. While it has served its purpose in the past, it will require a substantial investment of time and resources to return to the road.",
