    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I'm parting ways with my trusty ride, and it has been such a joy to drive. It's in really nice shape and has been super reliable for me\u2014perfect for someone looking for a solid, well-cared-for car that's ready to hit the road today. It runs great and looks even better in person! I'd love for it to go to a good home, so feel free to reach out if you have any questions or want to come take a look!",
