    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "This 996-generation Carrera 4S retains its mechanical integrity, featuring the naturally aspirated 3.6L flat-six with VarioCam Plus valve timing. The G96 six-speed manual gearbox offers precise gate engagement, paired with the factory-spec permanent all-wheel-drive system utilizing a viscous clutch center differential. Chassis dynamics remain sharp thanks to the wide-body Turbo-spec suspension geometry and staggered 18-inch 'Turbo Twist' alloys. Braking performance is anchored by four-piston monoblock calipers over cross-drilled rotors. Meticulously maintained with a documented service history addressing the IMS bearing and rear main seal, this example represents a balanced synergy of analog feedback and modern performance.",
      "price": 36500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 35
    },
    {
