    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "This meticulously maintained vehicle offers a perfect blend of reliability and style. The exterior retains a deep, lustrous shine, though you may find a few minor stone chips on the front bumper\u2014honest evidence of its time on the road. Inside, the cabin is a smoke-free sanctuary; the premium leather seats show gentle softening consistent with responsible use, but remain free of tears or heavy stains. Every feature, from the dual-zone climate control to the premium sound system, functions exactly as intended. Under the hood, the engine runs smoothly, a testament to a consistent service history. The transmission shifts seamlessly through every gear, and the brakes provide firm, confident stopping power. This is a solid, dependable choice for a buyer looking for a vehicle that has been treated with genuine respect and is ready for many more miles of trouble-free driving.",
      "price": 34500.0,
